.pac/
*.tmp.pac

# Solution packaging artifacts (we commit unpacked solution, not zips)
*.zip
!docs/**/*.zip
solution/bin/
solution/obj/
solution/temp/

# pac solution unpack output cache
**/SolutionPackage/
**/SolutionExport/

# Power Platform Build Tools artifacts
out/
out-debug/

